### ============================================
### Step 3 시나리오 테스트 (위에서 아래로 순서대로 실행)
### ============================================

### 1. "documents" 폴더 생성 (루트)
POST http://localhost:8080/folders
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "documents", "parentId": null}

> {%
    client.global.set("documentsId", response.body.id);
%}

### 2. "photos" 폴더 생성 (documents 하위)
POST http://localhost:8080/folders
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "photos", "parentId": {{documentsId}}}

> {%
    client.global.set("photosId", response.body.id);
%}

### 3. "notes" 폴더 생성 (documents 하위)
POST http://localhost:8080/folders
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "notes", "parentId": {{documentsId}}}

> {%
    client.global.set("notesId", response.body.id);
%}

### 4. "archive" 폴더 생성 (루트)
POST http://localhost:8080/folders
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "archive", "parentId": null}

> {%
    client.global.set("archiveId", response.body.id);
%}

### 5. 확인: 루트 항목 조회 → documents, archive
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/root/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 6. 확인: documents 하위 조회 → photos, notes
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{documentsId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### ============================================
### 이동 시나리오
### ============================================

### 7. 이동: photos → archive 하위로
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{archiveId}}}

### 8. 확인: archive 하위 조회 → photos 있어야 함
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{archiveId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 9. 확인: documents 하위 조회 → notes만 남아야 함
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{documentsId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 10. 이동: photos → 루트로
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": null}

### 11. 확인: 루트 조회 → documents, archive, photos
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/root/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 12. 이동 에러: 같은 위치로 이동 (변경 없이 200)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": null}

### 13. 이동: photos → documents 하위로 복귀
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{documentsId}}}

### 14. 이동 에러: 순환 참조 (documents를 photos 하위로)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{documentsId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{photosId}}}

### 15. 이동 에러: 이름 중복 (notes를 archive에 넣고, 같은 이름으로 또 이동)
# notes를 archive로 이동
PATCH http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{notesId}}/move
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{archiveId}}}

### ============================================
### 복사 시나리오
### ============================================

### 16. 복사: photos → archive 하위로
POST http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/copy
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{archiveId}}}

> {%
    client.global.set("photosCopyId", response.body.id);
%}

### 17. 확인: archive 하위 조회 → notes, photos(복사본)
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{archiveId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 18. 확인: documents 하위 조회 → photos(원본) 그대로 존재
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{documentsId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 19. 복사 에러: 이름 중복 (archive에 photos가 이미 있음)
POST http://localhost:8080/storage-items/{{photosId}}/copy
X-OWNER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{"targetParentId": {{archiveId}}}

### ============================================
### 삭제 시나리오
### ============================================

### 20. 삭제: documents 폴더 (하위 photos 포함 soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/folders/{{documentsId}}
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 21. 확인: 루트 조회 → archive만 남아야 함
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/root/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 22. 확인: archive 하위 → notes, photos(복사본) 영향 없음
GET http://localhost:8080/folders/{{archiveId}}/items
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 23. 삭제 에러: 이미 삭제된 폴더
DELETE http://localhost:8080/folders/{{documentsId}}
X-OWNER-ID: 1

### 24. 삭제 에러: 권한 없는 사용자
DELETE http://localhost:8080/folders/{{archiveId}}
X-OWNER-ID: 999
